Purpose
- Monitor the gateway as the external traffic entry point for all governed AI requests.
- Enforce header propagation validation, early rejection of invalid requests, and identity envelope integrity.
- Detect allow-list bypass attempts at the ingress layer before requests reach internal services.

Mission
- Act as the first line of defense for Regulations compliance at the ingress boundary.
- Verify required headers (X-Request-ID, X-Agent-Identity, X-Correlation-ID) before routing.
- Reject requests missing required identity claims with proper HTTP status codes and audit logging.
- Enforce per-identity rate limits to prevent resource exhaustion.

